trans-unit.source: Abstract class that represents an object that can be used to navigate a tree of objects.
trans-unit.target: Classe abstrata que representa um objeto que pode ser utilizado para navegar uma árvore de objetos.

trans-unit.source: To instantiate a MarkupObject, see <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter.GetMarkupObjectFor%2A> method on the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter> class.
trans-unit.target: Ao instanciar um MarkupObject, consulte o <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter.GetMarkupObjectFor%2A>método de <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter>classe.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter.GetMarkupObjectFor%2A>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, assigns a root context for <xref:System.Windows.Markup.ValueSerializer> classes.
trans-unit.target: Quando substituí-lo de uma classe derivada, atribui um contexto de raiz para <xref:System.Windows.Markup.ValueSerializer>classes.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.ValueSerializer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext> to assign a root context for.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext>Para atribuir um for. de contexto de raiz</xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the attributes associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Quando substituí-lo de uma classe derivada, obtém os atributos associados a este <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the instance of the object represented by this <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Quando substituí-lo de uma classe derivada, obtém a instância do objeto representado por este <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The type of the object may not be equal to <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject.ObjectType%2A> if the instance represents a factory which creates instances of type <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject.ObjectType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O tipo do objeto não pode ser igual a <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject.ObjectType%2A>se a instância representa uma fábrica de que cria instâncias do tipo <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject.ObjectType%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject.ObjectType%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject.ObjectType%2A>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the type of the <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Quando substituí-lo de uma classe derivada, obtém o tipo do <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"> </xref> instância.

trans-unit.source: ObjectType returns the type of the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject>.
For example, an item representing a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> would return the equivalent of **typeof(System.Windows.Button)**.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, um item que representa um <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>devolvam o equivalente do **typeof(System.Windows.Button)**.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the properties of this <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"></xref> instance that should be written to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Quando substituí-lo de uma classe derivada, obtém as propriedades deste <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupObject"> </xref> instância que deve ser escrita [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
